  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire and train your heroes to resist the attacks of monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Final Resistance 2\" is a tower defense Roguelike game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players develop heroes through random skills and equipment attributes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is divided into 2 stages:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Preparation Stage: Hire and upgrade heroes, forge equipment, and fully arm your heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >War Stage: Deploy your heroes and do everything possible to defend your castle.</p>",
